---

<section class="methodology-section">
  <Image src={Terapia1} class="bg-shape" alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" aria-hidden="true" />
  
  <div class="container">
    <header class="methodology-header">
      <h2>A metodologia que uso baseia-se na abordagem da <span class="dest1">Terapia Cognitivo-Comportamental (TCC) e terapias contextuais (ACT/DBT).</span> Elas são guiadas pela Prática Baseada em Evidências (PBE).</h2>
      <p>A TCC é um tipo de terapia que ajuda as pessoas a lidarem com seus pensamentos, sentimentos <br class="hide-mobile" />e comportamentos de uma forma mais saudável. Ela funciona assim:</p>
    </header>

    <div class="methodology-steps">
      {steps.map((step) => (
        <article class="step-row">
          <h3 class="step-title">{step.title}</h3>
          
          <div class="step-content">
            <div class="step-icon" set:html={step.icon} />
            <p class="step-desc">{step.desc}</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* --- Seção Base --- */
  .methodology-section {
    background-image: url('../../assets/divisor-03-1.webp');
    background-position: bottom center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
    background-size: contain;
    position: relative;
    padding: 90px 20px 200px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  /* Ilustração Absoluta no Topo Esquerdo */
  .bg-shape {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 10%;
    min-width: 80px;
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1140px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* --- Cabeçalho --- */
  .methodology-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .methodology-header h2 {
    font-family: "DM Serif Text", serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.5em;
    color: #0B4491;
    margin: 0 0 15px 0;
  }

  .dest1 {
    color: #0B4491;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .methodology-header p {
    font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: #0B4491;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* --- Container dos Passos --- */
  .methodology-steps {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .step-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 30px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #FCA3B9;
  }

  .step-row:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  /* --- Título da Esquerda --- */
  .step-title {
    font-family: "DM Serif Text", serif;
    font-size: 36px;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.2em;
    color: #0B4491C;
    margin: 0;
    flex: 1;
    padding-right: 20px;
  }

  /* --- Bloco com Ícone e Fundo Rosa (Direita) --- */
  .step-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: row;
    align-items: center;
    max-width: 530px;
    width: 100%;
    position: relative;
  }

  /* Este ::before recria perfeitamente o background rosa atrás do texto com o ícone transpassando */
  .step-content::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    left: 20px;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    width: calc(100% - 20px);
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #D94881;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .step-icon {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .step-icon :global(svg) {
    width: 110px;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .step-desc {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    font-family: "Open Sans", sans-serif;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 400;
    color: #F9F2EC;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 15px 20px 15px 15px;
  }

  /* --- Responsividade --- */
  @media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .step-row {
      gap: 30px;
    }
    
    .step-content {
      max-width: 450px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {

    .bg-shape {
      display: none;
    }

    .step-desc {
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.2em;
      padding: 10px 10px;
    }

    .methodology-section {
      padding: 50px 20px 100px;
    }

    .methodology-header{
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .methodology-header h2 {
      font-size: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hide-mobile {
      display: none;
    }

    .step-row {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 20px;
      padding: 20px 0;
    }

    .step-title {
      padding-right: 0;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .step-content {
      max-width: 100%;
    }

    .step-icon :global(svg) {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .step-content::before {
      left: 15px;
      width: calc(100% - 15px);
    }
  }
</style>